Package: qshot
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-pyqt6, python3-requests, python3-pil, python3-pip
Description: Screenshot and Annotation Tool
 QShot is a screenshot and annotation tool inspired by Lightshot.
 It allows you to capture a screen region, annotate it with pen,
 rectangle, arrow, and text tools, then save, copy, or upload to Imgur.
Features:
 - Region selection for screenshots
 - Annotation tools: Pen, Rectangle, Arrow, Text, Line
 - Multi-step undo/redo
 - Zoom and pan
 - Copy/paste annotations
 - Save, copy to clipboard, or upload to Imgur
